            Written in latine aboue an hundred yeares paſt, by the learned and right honorable maiſter Forteſcue knight, lorde Chauncellour of Englād in ye time of Kinge Henrye the .vi. And newly tranſlated into Engliſhe by Robert Mulcaſter.
         
         
            
